# Airtable Configuration (Recommended)
# 1. Create a free account at https://airtable.com
# 2. Create a base called "Wedding RSVP"
# 3. Create a table with fields: Name, Email, Phone, Guest_Count, Event
# 4. Create a Personal Access Token at https://airtable.com/create/tokens
#    - Add scopes: data.records:read, data.records:write
#    - Add access to your "Wedding RSVP" base
# 5. Get your Base ID from the API documentation or your base URL

VITE_AIRTABLE_API_KEY=your_personal_access_token_here
VITE_AIRTABLE_BASE_ID=your_base_id_here

# Google Sheets Fallback (Optional)
# If Airtable is not configured, you can use Google Sheets
# 1. Create a Google Sheet
# 2. Deploy a Google Apps Script as a Web App
# 3. Add the deployed URL here

VITE_GOOGLE_SHEETS_URL=your_google_sheets_script_url_here
